{"tid":1514870,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"8.30集會促停帶警犬上前線　總警司：睇唔到警犬身體有任何問題","createTime":"2019-08-29T02:27:36.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-30T10:57:40.000Z","uid":184679,"like":7,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"79449e0a1bed7f90cc44467021fbefd774ada4b7","tid":1514870,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-29T02:27:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/3212715/org/abf5a87fb5dcd21982e28e4a2d316652.jpg/YriarS4yCCTfGWrJBybZ6prS5sokoO9nojw2TaI8Nk0\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F3212715%2Forg%2Fabf5a87fb5dcd21982e28e4a2d316652.jpg%2FYriarS4yCCTfGWrJBybZ6prS5sokoO9nojw2TaI8Nk0&h=042ae9e2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n反對修訂逃犯條例風波持續，動物醫護界擬於本周五（30日）發起集會，抗議警方運用警犬處理示威活動，以及濫發催淚彈危及動物。有關集會已獲警方發出不反對通知書。<br />\n<br />\n警察公共關係科總警司謝振中今天（28日）在警方記者會上回應提問時指，警犬出動時有充足考慮，亦有嚴格指引，他又指目前並沒警犬受傷：「暫時睇唔到警犬身體有任何問題！」不過，對於警犬有否防止吸入催淚煙的裝備，謝振中就沒有回答。<br />\n<br />\n周五遮打花園集會<br />\n<br />\n自六月起，反修例示威活動持續，警民衝突不斷升級，警方多次於民居範圍發射催淚彈以驅散示威者。然而，催淚氣體同時令不少流浪動物，以及寵物受害。警方亦被拍攝到數度帶同警犬於示威現場出動，引起動保人士不滿。<br />\n<br />\n動物醫護界擬於本周五晚（30日）在中環遮打花園舉行集會，促請警方停止濫用暴力及保障動物權益。大會指，屆時將有獸醫、獸醫助護、獸醫學生、狗隻訓練員、動物護理員，以及市民參加是次集會。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/3212708/org/6196713295fbc89f623e32c54eee073d.jpg/jwX5QbUQ2TCcU1zQnIXMzyREinObEjIb7-5Df-_uQ38\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F3212708%2Forg%2F6196713295fbc89f623e32c54eee073d.jpg%2FjwX5QbUQ2TCcU1zQnIXMzyREinObEjIb7-5Df-_uQ38&h=c0711bf3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/3212720/org/43d46e17427dd23c21c562352d8148fa.jpg/tSDC5kCNn7dIH9Y2XKvTcRoll2Q0VOlmrBM9m6wTPZs\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F3212720%2Forg%2F43d46e17427dd23c21c562352d8148fa.jpg%2FtSDC5kCNn7dIH9Y2XKvTcRoll2Q0VOlmrBM9m6wTPZs&h=0ebd996a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<pre><code data-type=\"\">https://www.hk01.com/%E5%AF%B5%E7%89%A9/368926/8-30%E9%9B%86%E6%9C%83%E4%BF%83%E5%81%9C%E5%B8%B6%E8%AD%A6%E7%8A%AC%E4%B8%8A%E5%89%8D%E7%B7%9A-%E7%B8%BD%E8%AD%A6%E5%8F%B8-%E7%9D%87%E5%94%94%E5%88%B0%E8%AD%A6%E7%8A%AC%E8%BA%AB%E9%AB%94%E6%9C%89%E4%BB%BB%E4%BD%95%E5%95%8F%E9%A1%8C#media_id=3212720</code></pre>"},{"pid":"a6f87b0df435119e02186fbec56e9f27b44bcd93","tid":1514870,"uid":46457,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-29T02:28:43.000Z","msg":"屌你老母害死D狗狗，生命黎架，你班撚樣就當工具！"},{"pid":"6aa0c91733578a98656a66764870a2623e8a56cb","tid":1514870,"uid":43041,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-29T02:29:00.000Z","msg":"我已經分唔到講緊警犬定係警犬，<br />\n<br />\n以後有警犬既新聞，可唔可以寫&ldquo;真警犬&rdquo;<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/notcry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"083aa93594a4534dc8b65c6a06cd137c0806dc35","tid":1514870,"uid":271234,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-29T02:39:05.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\">【眾籌 Google 廣告】 本地文宣 : 多媒體廣告</span><br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1491396\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1491396</a>"},{"pid":"6ac28907939d7b41dcb53e5c5c84cd024400f9fc","tid":1514870,"uid":184679,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-29T05:23:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bark.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bark.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bark.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"64b06662c1daf758407a6ed475f3a65693bbb909","tid":1514870,"uid":37504,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-29T05:26:04.000Z","msg":"死黑警唔好再虐待動物呀"},{"pid":"a7a86cf7c332c564e48e8d1b07b7d90ddf604dd3","tid":1514870,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-29T13:05:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5c96b1a54a4b63be5b4e02